 <name>Lapiz</name>
 <summary>A Text Editor for the CAFE desktop environment</summary>
 <description>
  <p>
   Lapiz is a small, but powerful text editor designed specifically for
   the CAFE desktop. It has most standard text editor functions and fully
   supports international text in Unicode. Advanced features include syntax
   highlighting and automatic indentation of source code, printing and editing
   of multiple documents in one window.
  </p>
  <p>
   Lapiz is extensible through a plugin system, which currently includes
   support for spell checking, comparing files, viewing CVS ChangeLogs, and
   adjusting indentation levels.
  </p>
 </description>
